metadata.name: Galactik Burn
metadata.description:
This NFT Galactic Burn an animated depiction of a celestial goddess whose brain is composed of stars and galaxies. The artwork captures the wonder and beauty of the cosmos and presents it in a unique  view that captures the beauty of the universe.

In the future this will be a  "burnable edition," to exchange for another NFT or the same style a theme that will be more rare edition. 

3 per wallet burn two receive a new nft after January 31st 

The burn date of January 31st represents a celebration of life for me. 
1.31.2009 Is the day I experienced a TBI traumatic brain injury resulting in 12 days coma 
This my way of giving back with the gift of art
